docs.lead_paragraph: SANTIAGO, Chile, April 25-- President Joao Goulart of Brazil wound up a three-day visit today and could look back on a triumph in personal and political relations. He came in contact with nearly everyone from President to workers in their new low-cost homes and seemed to have conquered all.
